        services_text2_dermatology: "The department provides effective solutions for chronic skin conditions such as eczema, acne, and skin pigmentation, as well as skin rejuvenation through advanced laser techniques.The medical team consists of dermatology specialists, supported by modern technology to ensure excellent and safe results.",
